726934f-b.title: Queens: Ithaca Street - Whitney Avenue
726934f-b.text:
Ithaca Street, adjoining the S.E. corner of Whitney Avenue,
showing St. Bartholomews Roman Catholic Church, a new edifice.
The parochial school is behind the church, on Judge Street.
P. L. Sperr  April 25, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
